<window id="demo" xmlns:h="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
	<vbox width="100%">
		<html><![CDATA[
			<h4>Scripts</h4>
			<p>The Java language (NOT JavaScript) is the default page scripting language in our system. 
			The Java codes contained in the zscript element is executed when the page is rendered.</p>
			<p>The example script is executed and changes the label's value  from "Hello, World!" to "Hello, Script!".</p>
		]]></html>
		<groupbox mold="3d" width="100%">
			<caption label="View"><button label="Reload" height="18px" use="org.zkoss.zkdemo.userguide.ReloadButton"/></caption>
			<window id="view">
			</window>
		</groupbox>
		<groupbox id="tryView" mold="3d" open="false" width="100%">
			<caption label="Source"><button label="Try me!" use="org.zkoss.zkdemo.userguide.TryMeButton"/></caption>
			<textbox id="codeView" use="org.zkoss.zkdemo.userguide.CodeView" class="code" rows="15" width="100%">
				<attribute name="value"><![CDATA[
<window title="ZScript Demo" border="normal" width="200px">
	<label id="mylabel" value="Hello, World!"/>
	<zscript>
		mylabel.value = "Hello, Script!";
	</zscript>
</window>
				]]></attribute>
			</textbox>
		</groupbox>
	</vbox>
</window>
